lines.text: She send hordes of rats to granaries, put the evil eye on crops and gardens, make the women infertile...
What a nonsence! Rats because of less of cats. Poor crops because of caterpillars. And what about women, they'd better find fertilfull men. As easy as ABC.
Herr Organist, please suggest the idea to your son that presistition is a sin. And most of it is a presistition in a sin.
Wild Hunt! Beware of Wild Hunt!
